{
  "stem": "1029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even when I was in the concentration camp and so on, everything was through the eyes of a child who was eight who goes through these crises who remembers everything but who didn't-- who wasn't afraid because he was with his mother.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I wouldn't have had my mother, it could have been a different, very traumatic thing for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I was lucky that I always had my mother with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And even when I, I-- with my knowledge, with cerebral-- cerebrally, I knew that we will never survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It still didn't mean too much to me because I was still with my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother had such a hold over me, and she created this aura of safety.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There may have been something which may have been important to me, but I, I must tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can't make anything up because it wouldn't be nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't rem-- that part, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that we went and we had a hard time settling because the poorer families naturally got the poorer spots, you know, in the rooms that were available.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the better heeled families always got the better spots, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember we had a hard time settling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, there were about 110, 118 families, you know, in the-- in Totkomlos at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you get to the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we had a small town, remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a small town, like if you'd go to-- what could you call a small town just outside of Toronto?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not even Belleville.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, Belleville is really a big town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm talking about--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a short walk to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
